---
title: Stovetop Pastitsio-Inspired Pork Fusilli with Greek-Style 'Béchamel' Sauce
description: Inspired by the classic Greek layered pasta dish pastitsio, this stovetop version takes a fraction of the time to put together. Our Turkish Spice Blend lends this dish warm notes to give it the flavours we expect from the traditional version!
